    <item>
      <title>以色列人担心西岸动荡局势的袭击将引发更大范围的战争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israelis-fear-attack-from-restive-west-bank-will-spark-wider-war</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哈马斯袭击以色列南部、引发加沙战争并颠覆地区地缘政治格局已近一年，人们越来越担心巴勒斯坦武装分子可能从西岸发动类似入侵，引发更大范围的冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/israelis-fear-attack-from-restive-west-bank-will-spark-wider-war</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:30:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>阿拉巴马州警方称伯明翰深夜枪击事件造成四人死亡</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</link>
      <description><![CDATA[阿拉巴马州伯明翰（美联社）——据警方和新闻报道，阿拉巴马州伯明翰市一处夜生活区发生枪击事件，造成 4 人死亡，20 多人受伤。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/4-killed-in-late-night-shooting-in-birmingham-alabama-police-say</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 07:25:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>金正恩在与俄罗斯交好的同时，对中国给予了温和的赞扬</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/kim-jong-un-offers-tepid-praise-to-china-as-he-cozies-up-to-russia</link>
      <description><![CDATA[朝鲜领导人金正恩以看似克制的言辞向中国国家主席习近平致以问候，而当前平壤正与俄罗斯走得更近，减少对其长期亚洲盟友的依赖。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-22/kim-jong-un-offers-tepid-praise-to-china-as-he-cozies-up-to-russia</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 06:30:08 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列突袭并关闭半岛电视台西岸新闻局</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/urgent-israel-raids-and-shuts-down-al-jazeera-s-bureau-in-ramallah-in-the-west-bank</link>
      <description><![CDATA[迪拜，阿拉伯联合酋长国（美联社）——周日凌晨，以色列军队突袭了卫星新闻网络半岛电视台位于以色列占领的约旦河西岸的办公室，勒令该电视台关闭。以色列正在扩大针对这家卡塔尔资助的广播公司的行动，因为它报道了加沙地带的以色列与哈马斯战争。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2024-09-22/urgent-israel-raids-and-shuts-down-al-jazeera-s-bureau-in-ramallah-in-the-west-bank</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 22 Sep 2024 01:58:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
